title: Objkt4Objkt
description: Community art event to celebrate the creativity and talent in the space! Participation is simple: mint 1 piece, as a large or open edition, on any Tezos platform, for free or low price (up to 1tez). To be included in this event page, you must add "OBJKT4OBJKT" as a tag at mint time. We would like to kindly remind everyone to only take 1 edition of any artwork you collect.
